        <item>
            <title>1.4.4</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 22:12:12 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>12</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Changes
- Rate limit bars now display at 0% instead of being hidden when rate limited, making limits always visible
- Improved extension update detection to better check for new versions

### Bug Fixes
- Fixed new windows opening at minimum size (400×600) when no other windows were open; now restores previous window size or uses a proper default (500×800)
]]></description>
