        <item>
            <title>1.4.3</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 10:52:19 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>11</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Changes
- Status bar now shows the Sonnet-only weekly rate limit when using a Sonnet model, instead of the all-models weekly limit. Falls back to the all-models limit when Sonnet-specific data is not available.
]]></description>
